                <p>This summative assessment evaluates three MYP criteria:</p>

                <div class="criterion-grid">
                    <div class="criterion-box">
                        <div class="criterion-label">Criterion A: Analysing</div>
                        <p>Your understanding of genre conventions, historical context, and thematic connections</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="criterion-box">
                        <div class="criterion-label">Criterion C: Producing Text</div>
                        <p>Your creativity, imagination, and development of your protagonist</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="criterion-box">
                        <div class="criterion-label">Criterion D: Using Language</div>
                        <p>Your vocabulary, sentence structure, grammar, and professional register throughout</p>
